<html t:type="layout" title="Science Olympiad"
      xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_4.xsd"
        >

    <div class="bodyContent">
    	<img class="center" src="${asset:context:images/SCI_OLY_LOGO.jpeg}" alt="Image Not Found"/>
    	
    	<h3>Welcome</h3>
    	<p class="index">
    		We welcome to the NDSU Science Olympiad Scoring web software. 
    		This site was built with the intension of assisting in the scoring process of the annual Science Olympiad contest held on the NDSU campus.
    		It features a number of pages built to make adding new scores, adjusting previous scores, and viewing contest information as straight forward and intuitive as possible.
    		We hope you enjoy this product!
    	</p>
    	
    	<h3>Getting Started</h3>
    	<p class="index">
    		The first thing you'll want to do is click the "Sign In" button located at the top right corner of the site.
    		<br/><br/>
    		<img class="center" style="border: 0.1em solid black;" src="${asset:context:images/INDEX_LOGIN_BUTTON.png}" alt="Image Not Found"/>
    		<br/>
    		This will bring you to the Login page where you can sign in to the site with your user account.
    		
    	</p>
    	
    </div>


</html>
